#### [MODIFY] [file_parse_service.py](file:///c:/Users/Osama/ascend-academy/backend/services/file_parse_service.py)

In the [parse_pdf](file:///c:/Users/Osama/ascend-academy/backend/services/file_parse_service.py#8-60) loop, **after extracting raw text** but **before calling AI**:
1. Call `is_metadata_slide(raw_text)`.
2. If `True`: skip AI enhancement/summary/quiz generation entirely. Set `summary = ""` and `questions = []` (empty). Still keep the slide in the output so the student can see the original content, but mark it with an empty summary/quiz so the frontend knows it's a metadata slide.

