In the [generate_summary_endpoint](file:///c:/Users/Osama/ascend-academy/backend/api/ai_content.py#30-40) and [generate_quiz_endpoint](file:///c:/Users/Osama/ascend-academy/backend/api/ai_content.py#41-51), add a pre-check:
1. Run `is_metadata_slide(body.slide_text)` on the incoming text.
2. If `True`, return a specific response (`"summary": "This slide contains administrative information only."` / a fallback quiz with empty question) **without** calling the AI model. This saves API tokens and avoids bad output.

